Quiz title: DevOps Chapter 1

1. True or false: a system or record is a system in which customers can access directly 
and use to interact with the business
*a) True
b) false

2. which one of these is not return on investment of DevOPs
a) Enhanced customer experience 
b) Increased capacity to innovate 
c) Faster time to value
*d) Happier work environment

3. which one of these is not a DevOPs adoption principle
a) Develop and test against production-like systems 
b) Deploy with repeatable, reliable processes 
c) Monitor and validate operational quality 
*d) Decrease feedback loops

4. True or false: when it comes to monitoring metrics should be captured in a format that all business stakeholders can understand and use.
*a) True
b) false
